Author: Lozzibee30
Text: Ugh I feel your pain. My beloved brand of vegetable gyoza have been discontinued and all the other ones are just not the same.

Author: daniel_silva2
Text: That's always a bummer.  Still remember when my favourite cream cheese spread went from 200 to 320 kcal. Those fuckers....  Honestly, you just have to move on and find new foods.
